name: Zenithereum
description: Zenithereum is a decentralized AI protocol that aims to advance the field of AI and provide benefits for humanity. The focus of the project is on researching and developing AI tools that can help agents grow and thrive in both crypto and real-world environments. With its decentralized approach, Zenithereum seeks to provide a secure and transparent platform for AI development and deployment. The goal of the project is to enhance agent performance and provide a range of applications and services that can improve the lives of people around the world. Whether it's through improving supply chain management, enhancing financial services, creating new forms of digital identity, or another application, Zenithereum aims to use the power of AI and blockchain technology to benefit humanity. The project is at the forefront of a rapidly evolving field and holds great potential for creating positive change in the world.
